"CES is an ideal venue to reach new customers both domestic and international.  Atlantic Technology had the most confirmed appointments in years thanks to the creative marketing skills of the CEA group in creating a most successful attendance and level of organization.  2004 CES - A wonderful upbeat mood!"
<p>
Joseph P. Clayton, president and CEO, Sirius Satellite Radio, New York, NY
"The best show in terms of attendance, energy, news coverage and new customers in my 30 years in the consumer electronics industry."
<p>
